Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.24,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mid-terms
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.24,0:00:02.74,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ranking Announcement
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.87,0:00:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What rank am I? What rank am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.16,0:00:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act so giddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:12.92,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,63 - Raku Ichijo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.25,0:00:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, only 63rd out of 207?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.84,0:00:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's it gonna take\Nto crack the Top 50, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.63,0:00:21.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! There I am! There I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.13,0:00:22.13,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,6 - Seishiro Tsugumi  \N  5 - Chitoge Kirisaki
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.43,0:00:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Darn... only No. 5?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.43,0:00:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not that I really\Nstudied that hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.64,0:00:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm next to Young Mistress!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.14,0:00:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn you prodigies!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.23,0:00:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How'd it go, Ichijo?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.40,0:00:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Onodera!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.69,0:00:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.77,0:00:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was No. 88. Well, I guess\Nit's the same as usual for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.44,0:00:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I did so-so myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:43.66,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,23 - Ruri Miyamoto\N22 - Shu Maiko
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.95,0:00:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! We're\Nside by side, huh, Ruri?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.16,0:00:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.62,0:00:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maiko gets really good grades!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ruri!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.75,0:00:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's always like that, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.04,0:00:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Irritating as it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.00,0:01:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Come to think of it, I haven't\Nspotted Tachibana's name yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.80,0:01:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.26,0:01:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder where she's at?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.30,0:01:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing her, I bet\Nshe's right near the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.68,0:01:08.93,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,185 - Marika Tachibana
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.18,0:01:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what's up with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.74,0:02:51.74,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Teach Me"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:55.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm embarrassed to say it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.62,0:02:58.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but studying has never\Nbeen my strong suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.62,0:03:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? Well, who would've thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.79,0:03:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You seem like the type who'd have\Nno trouble with that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.71,0:03:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I have zero motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.05,0:03:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really are being honest there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.51,0:03:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For a long time, in order to become\Nyour bride, Master Raku...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,all my efforts have\Ngone into various lessons,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.60,0:03:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and how to become as attractive\Na woman as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you wouldn't just blurt out\Nstuff that makes us all freeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.36,0:03:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but you can't just keep hanging on\Nwith grades like these, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You could end up getting held back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The teacher said if I got below 40 points\Non my next math test, I'd have to re-take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.33,0:03:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know, Master Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.12,0:03:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind, could you\Ntutor me at my home after school?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you study by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.34,0:03:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll thank you not to\Nunderestimate my ineptitude!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't possibly improve my grades\Nwithout someone's guidance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.02,0:03:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:04:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, why don't\NI tutor you myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.02,0:04:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's more fitting for\Nsomeone ranked No. 5 like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.98,0:04:06.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, surely you jest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.27,0:04:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't seem like you know the first\Nthing about teaching others, Kirisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.24,0:04:12.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, Master Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:13.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mind, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since my father won't be\Ncoming home tonight,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we should be able to study\Nto our heart's content till daybreak!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.91,0:04:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Till daybreak?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, let's not\Nget ahead of ourselves, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.92,0:04:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I don't mind helping you out\Nwith your schoolwork...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.75,0:04:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But spending the night is\Ngoing overboard, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, regarding that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since the math test is tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was it tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.85,0:04:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'd forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.39,0:04:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Kirisaki tagging along, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.48,0:04:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All you're doing is having\Nfriends over to study for a test,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.78,0:04:53.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so what's wrong with me\Nbeing around, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.82,0:04:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing wrong with it, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if I may be blunt... you're\Nlike a third wheel, should I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be blunt\Nabout that kind of thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, I'm glad you're here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.09,0:05:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, get ready to study, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.38,0:05:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll help you with whatever\Nyou don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as if you're going to\Nbe the one to teach me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.01,0:05:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll start then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand this problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heave-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No more fooling around!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.94,0:05:29.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to glom\Nonto him to learn, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.27,0:05:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I would learn faster\Nif I was next to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.86,0:05:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Man, thank goodness she's here, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.74,0:05:36.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.74,0:05:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Which part don't you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.66,0:05:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, factorization, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up. For this, you go like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think I understand it\Njust a little bit better now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, if this a is me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the b is you, Master Raku,\Nand the x is Kirisaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.09,0:05:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then all I have to do is\Nlock out just the x, like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That pisses me off, so\Ndon't memorize it that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.02,0:06:06.90,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Modern Japanese
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, Master Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind showing me\Nhow to do this, next?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Modern Japanese? What about math?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.07,0:06:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know how this lady feels, waiting for\Nher husband's return in this chapter...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:16.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, she's... See,\Nshe's not just waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.87,0:06:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's about to go off\Nand see him herself, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! That is correct, Master Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.87,0:06:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, on to the next problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.08,0:06:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is the correct\Nanswer you should give
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:33.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to a courageous girl who's cared for\Nher beloved for ten years?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes or yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.51,0:06:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Study, for God's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Oh, crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How do you solve this problem again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.27,0:06:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If the tutor himself doesn't\Nget it, how helpful is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.23,0:06:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way around it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.06,0:06:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where? Let me see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.90,0:06:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right. It's this problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.03,0:06:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just use a formula\Nlike you normally would...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:07:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, would you stop interfering?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, did you say interfere?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.91,0:07:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By that do you mean\Nto interfere your studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.37,0:07:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or a world where only you two exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.62,0:07:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If the latter, I have every intention of\Nhindering you as much as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you... are you\Nat all motivated to study?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.34,0:07:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't shape up,\Nyou really will repeat a grade!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.42,0:07:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not that I'm not motivated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.05,0:07:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I simply can't do what I cannot do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then, how did you\Nget into our high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you got in\Nthrough the backdoor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.48,0:07:32.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:35.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm only joking about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:38.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but the day before the entrance\Nexam, I pulled an all-nighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:42.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And thanks to that, I barely passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:43.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An all-nighter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.70,0:07:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wouldn't you say\Nthat in your case,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's not a matter of you\Nnot being a good student...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.33,0:07:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...just that you didn't\Nbother to study?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.79,0:07:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it seems to me that you'd start\Ngetting good grades if you really hit the books.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:08:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give it all you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.93,0:08:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do what I can to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to\Nget held back, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Master Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.10,0:08:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you'll miss me if\Nyou can't get promoted with me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.48,0:08:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do my best!\NThat makes me so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.23,0:08:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're not wrong about that,\Nbut you sure took it in a positive way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But for some reason, having you tutor me\Nlike this reminds me of those days 10 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, so you helped her\Nwith her schoolwork?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:33.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No... after all, I was\Nonly in kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.58,0:08:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master Raku taught me so many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.51,0:08:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Games that I could enjoy\Neven if I was alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.47,0:08:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was going on at kindergarten...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.97,0:08:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,he'd teach me the songs\Nand talk about his friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.51,0:08:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It really brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.82,0:09:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not cool, not cool...\NI totally nodded off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're both asleep,\Nfor crying out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.07,0:09:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, but I can't really blame them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I mean, it's the dead of night...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.58,0:09:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rakkun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rakkun, I adore you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.42,0:09:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Seriously, I don't know\Nwhat it is that she sees in me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's a pretty weird girl,\Nbut she's a good kid.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:26.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's hot and popular with the guys.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure she could\Nhave anyone she wanted.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Being told "I love you" by someone...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.81,0:09:35.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.35,0:09:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It feels so strange.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ohhh, Rakkun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.40,0:09:43.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's your biggest fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.28,0:09:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but as long as you're\Nokay with it, Rakkun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.16,0:09:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you - I know\Nyou're totally awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:09:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you have time to mess around\Nlike that, just go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.25,0:10:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work hard! I'll work hard, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.52,0:10:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This isn't good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.36,0:10:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I completely dozed off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Master Raku is very sweet, after all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So very warm...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.79,0:10:40.79,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take Note!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.39,0:10:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...really love you, Rakkun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I suppose pulling an all-nighter\Ncan only take me so far.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This really looks quite difficult.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But this is the problem\Nthat I did with Master Raku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.70,0:11:11.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So's this one...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.95,0:11:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and this one!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.91,0:11:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, my! This is wonderful!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.37,0:11:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I add up the answers that I'm sure\NI got right, it comes out to 40 exactly!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.25,0:11:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now I won't have to re-take the exam.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.17,0:11:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man, a 38?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You came so close, huh, Tachibana?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.01,0:11:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad, but you're gonna\Nhave to re-take the test, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.60,0:11:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, but considering you got a zero on your\Nlast math test, I'd say you did real good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.19,0:11:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.27,0:11:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Looks like she re-wrote this answer here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.78,0:11:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And she got it right the first time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Master Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:56.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, it looks like\NI'll have to re-take the exam,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.83,0:12:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so please tutor me again, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.54,0:12:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you! At least try to\Nstudy on your own a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.30,0:12:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're asking for the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, jeez...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right? Young Mistress...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Studying all night... you're\Npushing yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.81,0:12:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it takes too great a toll on you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.64,0:12:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.73,0:12:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing I can't handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.65,0:12:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It happened during that\NCulture Festival as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.77,0:12:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've been pushing\Nyourself too hard lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.28,0:12:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to tell me.\NI know that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:36.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than as your bodyguard,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am by your side to watch over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.62,0:12:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.42,0:12:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know that already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:53.76,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Master Raku"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.64,0:13:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you want me to take care of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. So sorry to trouble you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be away on a trip with\Nmy father for just one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.86,0:13:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.61,0:13:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I like taking care of animals anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.48,0:13:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to thank you\Nin some way, sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.66,0:13:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, does this little guy\Ntalk or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.74,0:13:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes! He's very smart, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Riiiight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Riiiight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.96,0:13:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, that's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:24.67,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To Master Raku\NA love note
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.92,0:13:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've summarized\Nhow to take care of him,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and what to watch out for in this note.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.88,0:13:32.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.63,0:13:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.55,0:13:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Master Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.60,0:13:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Master Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.36,0:13:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master Raku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.15,0:13:53.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why would she pick out\Na name like that, of all things?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.19,0:13:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if she's\Nneedling me or if she's serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:13:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Master Raku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.24,0:13:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master Raku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, you look like a dimwit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, this is depressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, we don't\Nhave parrots at school
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.96,0:14:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so this'll be my first time\Nlooking after one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.88,0:14:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're a parrot,\NI'd love to see you talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you about to say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Master Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.68,0:14:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's your biggest flaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.06,0:14:25.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really, Master Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.64,0:14:27.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So... bold... of... you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What does she think she's doing?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master Raku, you pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.74,0:14:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, heh, Marika...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Does it feel good there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that my line?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what the hell does\Nshe think she's doing?! That idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.33,0:14:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time to feed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:48.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.75,0:14:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's your favorite food!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.42,0:14:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why isn't he eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.55,0:14:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're hungry, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.88,0:14:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, the note says...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"How to Feed Master Raku."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:06.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Master Raku absolutely\Nwill not eat unless you say,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}'Here, Master Raku... ahhhhh!'\Nwith all your sincerity."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That girl... what kind of\Ntraining is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.65,0:15:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Master Raku...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.90,0:15:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.99,0:15:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did I ever end up like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But hey, never mind the content...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.71,0:15:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,this little guy can speak pretty fluently.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder if he'll learn\Nto say what I teach him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master Raku, you're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.84,0:15:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master Raku, you're so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.51,0:15:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that goes without saying!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really are amazing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.22,0:15:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, did you get what I just said?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.23,0:15:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your memorization skills are unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.02,0:15:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was practically a conversation!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.85,0:15:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm gonna make you\Nlearn no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.07,0:15:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Master Raku,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.82,0:16:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,try saying "How much wood would a woodchuck\Nchuck, if a woodchuck could chuck wood?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking to you, Master Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.91,0:16:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Master Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.16,0:16:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master... what's\Nup with that, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.45,0:16:10.96,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"How much wood would a woodchuck\Nchuck, if a woodchuck could chuck wood?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Naming his pet after himself,\Neven sticking on a "Master."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sure Young\NMaster has his reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:12.75,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Master Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.13,0:16:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a bust.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.13,0:16:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I got so caught up in\Nteaching him phrases.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:24.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And he never did learn\Nto say any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.64,0:16:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Master Raku? Where'd you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap, I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A pet that I was entrusted with!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.53,0:16:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where are you? Ma—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.74,0:16:49.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.71,0:16:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you are! Thank goodness\Nyou didn't get too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:17:01.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't, Master Raku!\NYou mustn't touch me there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.93,0:17:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what's the problem, Marika? Your\Nbody doesn't seem to be resisting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.89,0:17:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master Raku, you're so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.35,0:17:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, crap... I've got to do\Nsomething about this right away!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not even a matter of\NTachibana never forgiving me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.36,0:17:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My reputation around\Nthe neighborhood will be in shreds!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.07,0:17:25.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hold up, Master Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.07,0:17:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.78,0:17:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.49,0:17:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know you can always\Ncome to us with any problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.87,0:17:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is so sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.71,0:17:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave him be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master's in\Nthe throes of adolescence!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.67,0:17:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's heading downtown!\NThis is not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.76,0:17:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! What the...? You scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.26,0:17:47.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.64,0:17:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did it escape from somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But really, your face pisses me off\Nfor some reason, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You kind of remind of that moron...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.69,0:17:57.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, oh... Master Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:17:58.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.15,0:18:02.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't be so rough with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.07,0:18:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I don't\Nfind that attractive, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Marika, relax...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Chitoge?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Chitoge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Glad you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By any chance did\Na parrot come flying by?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.09,0:18:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was that... your parrot?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:25.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:27.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking care of him\Nfor Tachibana, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.80,0:18:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see which way he...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.31,0:18:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Make amends by\Ndying, you dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.18,0:18:35.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.77,0:18:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about your parrot?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go look for it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.02,0:18:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem, for Pete's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.77,0:18:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, I never have any\Nclue what she's thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.24,0:18:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn him... I swear I'm\Ngonna catch him this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.16,0:18:51.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap! That's Onodera!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.91,0:18:54.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a sweet parrot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where he came from?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.37,0:18:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did he escape from\Nsomewhere, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,0:18:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't we catch him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Mr. Parrot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here, boy! Here, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.84,0:19:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You really have a way with\Nany kind of animal, huh, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.72,0:19:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did you lose your way?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.89,0:19:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where your owner is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.06,0:19:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I belong to Master Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my beloved Marika!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.44,0:19:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My sweet honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really, I don't believe you, Master Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:29.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, was I too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up a second, Onodera!\NIt's not what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just hear me out and you'll see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.87,0:19:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's fine, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.62,0:19:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't heard anything, and I haven't\Nseen anything, so it's all good, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.88,0:19:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marika!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.92,0:19:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one that I love!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.80,0:19:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come back here, you dumbass bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.22,0:19:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Or I'll end up frying you\Nand eating you up, dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.51,0:19:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to set the record straight,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but if I don't go after him,\Nit'll mean more grief for me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.14,0:19:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I gotta catch him as soon as possible!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.98,0:20:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.48,0:20:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tsugumi! Glad I ran into you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.48,0:20:04.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Help me out, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.61,0:20:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See, there's this pet parrot...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.53,0:20:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.15,0:20:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've been with Marika Tachibana...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.82,0:20:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have... have you no shame?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She hit on me first!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Divine punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a bird! You're just a bird!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.50,0:20:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, I'm never gonna\Nget anywhere like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.21,0:20:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.96,0:20:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Does it say anything in that note?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:26.63,DefaultTop,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If Master Raku escapes,\Nthis is the retrieval process{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.13,0:20:27.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.05,0:20:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How can I do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.47,0:20:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell is she gonna\Nmake me yell all over town?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.76,0:20:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You come back here, Raku Ichijo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.31,0:20:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But unless I catch that bird,\NI can't make things right.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.52,0:20:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Say this in a loud voice?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.40,0:20:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.94,0:20:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.78,0:20:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My sweet honey, Marika!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.12,0:21:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I... love... you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.47,0:21:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was that, just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.72,0:21:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, it's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Shuei-gumi heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.76,0:21:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.76,0:21:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.26,0:21:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's youth for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! Master Raku?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.81,0:21:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing in a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.27,0:21:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Master Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.94,0:21:29.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's so good to see you looking well!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.07,0:21:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Were you a good parrot\Nwhile I was away?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.65,0:21:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marika! Marika!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.66,0:21:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.74,0:21:36.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.53,0:21:40.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Marika... Do you know what\Nthat parrot's been saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.54,0:21:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you shouldn't take\Nany of that at face value.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.79,0:21:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's so misleading!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.17,0:21:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.00,0:21:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank God...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.38,0:21:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything's all cleared up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.97,0:21:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, if you'll excuse me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.18,0:21:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master Raku, I'll\Nthank you another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.89,0:21:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.10,0:22:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For some reason, she left without\Nmaking a fuss today, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.77,0:22:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.94,0:22:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My sweet honey, Marika!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.12,0:22:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I... love... you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.62,0:22:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The operation was\Na resounding success!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.87,0:22:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then, Master Raku, I want you\Nto learn this phrase next.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.75,0:22:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And try to really nail it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.63,0:22:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My beloved Marika... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.05,0:22:36.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...love...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.09,0:22:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting the chills.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.26,0:22:40.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
